snippet.title: Aquaman 2 producer " Why is Amber Heard not fired yet"
snippet.description:
Aquaman 2 producer "Why is Amber Heard not fired yet"
The majority of people feel Zack Snyder's Justice League is only there to increase HBO Max subscriptions. Despite the fact that 70 million dollars for a remake of a failed film may seem like a lot of money, Netflix and Disney have consistently spent more on original material. Indeed, if Warner Bros. had bought into Snyder's original vision, Joss Whedon would not have had to reshoot 95 percent of the movie after Snyder had gone.
